title: Babysitting Bedlam/Rubbed the Wrong Way
description: Rubbed the Wrong Way: After a Bakugan field errupts the town kids stampede to get their own Bakugan but when the field is contaminated Lia must save the day./Babysitting Bedlam: Dan and Wynton meet a strange boy who leads them into an underground maze where they discover the boy's Bakugan has been enslaved.

title: Bakugan: Beyond the Brawl - Battle for the Joystick
description: Drago and Hydorous Brawl to see who will play the next video game, but wind up destroying Dan's controller and coffee table.

title: Bakugan: Behind the Battle - Artulean
description: Dan introduces us Lightning's Bakugan Partner Artulean, letting us know what makes his abilities so special.

title: Bakugan: Behind the Battle - Howlkor
description: Wynton introduces us to the three headed canine Bakugan and why he's a perfect partner to the everyone's favorite dog, Lightning.

title: Burger Run/Monkey See, Monkey Don't
description: Burger Run: When the local Burger Joint is being threatened by a rogue Bakugan, Dan steps up to save the day and the burgers!/Monkey See, Monkey Don't: The AO stop neighborhood kids from copycat behavior (namely, using their Bakugan for frivolous reasons).

title: Bakugan: Behind the Battle - Cyndeous
description: Dan introduces us and lets us why Cyndeous chose Dan to be his human partner. He also tells us why Cyndeous is a great warrior.

title: Dog Daze/In Focus
description: Dog Daze: Lightning discovers a new Bakugan, Artulean, leading to an unhealthy rivalry with Howlkor./In Focus: While Lia's newswoman mom does an expose on the AO Strata the Hunter tries to capture Hydorous.

title: Bakugan: Behind the Battle - Nillious
description: Magnus tells us why he thinks his two headed Bakugan Nillious is the dangerous creature to mess with.

title: Bakugan: Behind the Battle - Pegatrix
description: Lia shares the story on how she discovered her Bakugan Pegatrix, what makes her so unique and why she's a fierce warrior.

title: Mask of Power/Story Holes
description:
Mask of Power: Philomena Dusk from AAAnimus Corp. hires Magnus and gives him a control implant to bolster the power of his Bakugan to defeat Dan./Story Holes:  
A cryptic call leads the AO in search of a missing Bakugan but they soon realize the call was actually a test from a mysterious benefactor.

title: Bakugan: Beyond the Brawl - Teamwork - Makes the Dream Work
description: A trio of Awesome One Bakugan work together to overcome obstacles in the garage including Nillious.

title: Frenemies/Strata's Fear
description: Frenemies: Two new Bakugan Brawlers, Shun and Magnus, try out for the AO./Strata's Fear: The AO solve the mystery of a kid's missing Bakugan and meet a Bakugan Hunter named Strata.

title: The Exit/The Lost and the Cost
description: The Exit: The AO compete with a rival Brawling team for ViewTube hits leading to a "winner take all" brawl./The Lost and the Cost: Everett Ray, a promotor, tries to get the AO to join an official league for Bakugan Battling.

title: Bakugan: Beyond the Brawl - A Bakugan By Any Other Name
description: Pegatrix believes she is being disrespected so she challenges Two of her fellow Awesome One Bakugan to a battle.

title: Bakugan: Beyond the Brawl - Scorching Cold
description: Drago's cold halts a battle with Gorthion but inadvertently defeats Nillious.

title: Bakugan: Beyond the Brawl - Tin Pan Alley
description: Bakugan target practice becomes real with Nillious showing up.

title: Local Heroes/Pegatrix
description: Local Heroes: After the AO cause accidental destruction Dan's parents question whether the kids should be allowed to keep their Bakugan./Pegatrix: Lia disagrees with her new Bakugan Pegatrix on battle techniques but during a fierce fight Lia must rely on Pegatrix's battle savy.

title: Bakugan: Beyond the Brawl - Bedtime for Bakugan
description: Unable to sleep with Turtonium's snoring, Dragonoid resorts to strong measures to wake him.

title: Bakugan: Behind the Battle - Trox
description: Wynton introduces us to Trox, and tells us why he is the best Bakugan partner for him.

title: Bakugan: Beyond the Brawl - Take 23
description: Two Awesome Ones Bakugan film a faux battle only to be challenged to a real battle by two evil Bakugan.

title: Bakugan: Beyond the Brawl - Snack Attack
description: Two Awesome One Bakugan battle over a bag of chips.

title: Origin of Species
description: Origin of Species, Part 1: Dan meets his partner Bakugan Drago for the first time and we learn about the incident that happened on Earth twelve years ago./Origin of Species, Part 2: Dan and friends win the Bakugan Battle, firmly establishing the Awesome Ones as our heroes and Bakugan Brawlers.

title: Bakugan: Behind the Battle - Hydorous
description: Shun tells us about his main Bakugan Hydorous and what makes him such a formidable cobatant.

title: Mr. Moon/What's Wrong with Dan
description: Mr. Moon: Wynton finds a new Bakugan who proves difficult to control but things get more complicated when Col. Tripp seizes control of Trox./What's Wrong with Dan: With "Dan" behaving strangely toward the AO Lightning sniffs out the truth- an impostor!

title: Bakugan: Behind the Battle - Dragonoid
description: Dan introduces us to his number one Bakugan Drago, showcasing what makes him potentially the most powerful Bakugan ever.

title: Bakugan: Beyond the Brawl - Bad Bakugan Brawl
description: Nillious, Artulean and Maxotaur are going to ambush Drago but wind up getting into a Bakugan Brawl between themselves.

title: Bakugan: Behind the Battle - Gorthion
description: Lia let's us know about Gorthian the Bakugan special abilities and beyond his strength why she loves brawling with him on her side.

title: Bakugan: Behind the Battle - Mantonoid
description: Aay, one of the Awesome One's arch enemies, shows us Mantanoid special abilities.

title: Bully for You/Trolling for Laughs
description: Bully for You: The AO must handle a neighborhood bully who is using his Bakugan to pick on the local kids./Trolling for Laughs: Wynton's constant practical jokes wear thin on his Bakugan Trox so the Bakugan decide to teach him a lesson.
